Uses of Package
heif

  • Packages that use heif 
    Package Description
    heif
    Provides high-level classes for parsing and manipulating HEIF-based files.
    heif.boxes
    Classes for parsing and representing individual HEIF-structured boxes.
  • Classes in heif used by heif 
    Class and Description
    BoxHandler
    Handles parsing of HEIF/HEIC file structures based on the ISO Base Media Format.
    HeifBoxType
    Defines all supported HEIF (High Efficiency Image File) box types.
    HeifBoxType.BoxCategory
    Describes the general role of the box in the file structure.
  • Classes in heif used by heif.boxes 
    Class and Description
    HeifBoxType
    Defines all supported HEIF (High Efficiency Image File) box types.
